  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "2. Spread the charred poutine fries in a single layer on a baking sheet.",
    "3. Top the fries with the juicy cheese curds and gratin sauce.",
    "4. Sprinkle the grated gratin cheese over the top.",
    "5. Bake in the preheated oven for 10-12 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "6. Remove from the oven and sprinkle with chopped fresh parsley.",
    "7. Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "8. Serve hot and enjoy!"
